text: Franck Delhem was a fencer from Belgium. Delhem competed at the 1960 Summer Olympics. He was born on 2 May 1936 and died on 20 January 2020.Franck Delhem == References == Category:1936 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Belgian fencers Category:Olympians for Belgium Category:Sportspeople from Antwerp
